{"data": [{"id": "4743741", "title": "Tracking Baker Brothers Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pharmaceuticals Medical Stock Market Industry Sector Wall Street Buildings 3d Illustration\" data-id=\"1160060870\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5000px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">iQoncept</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to Baker Brothers\u2019 13F stock portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on Baker Brothers\u2019 regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1263508/000110465924118899/0001104659-24-118899-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F Form</a> filed on 11/14/2024. The</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743741-tracking-baker-brothers-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:38:23"}, {"id": "4743750", "title": "CPI Bullish For Long-Term Inflation Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with the words CPI on coins stack. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth with relate icon.\" data-id=\"1733234018\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Boy Wirat</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>CPI printed in-line at .3 on core and headline. Importantly, rent and owners' equivalent rent finally declined to .2 for the month. Other volatile components such as new and used cars, lodging and airline fares were elevated.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743750-cpi-bullish-for-long-term-inflation-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:20:00"}, {"id": "4743738", "title": "Sun Hung Kai Properties: A Solid Bet On Recovery In Hong Kong And China", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone view of Hong Kong city\" data-id=\"1267068394\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) c