idth=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ratana21</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This analysis takes the BLS inflation data and recalculates the percentage changes at the category level to get unrounded numbers. The total number ties to the BLS, but it gives more detail at the granular level.</p> <h2>November CPI</h2>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743743-cpi-shelter-prices-are-rising-4-7-percent-yoy", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 06:55:00"}, {"id": "4743736", "title": "IYR: Overlooked Real Estate Fundamentals And Technical Tailwinds Heading Into 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view over houses in Paris suburb\" data-id=\"1500297506\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Yeowell</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>Shares of companies from the Real Estate sector have struggled compared to the stout returns of the S&amp;P 500 in the last five years. COVID obviously dealt a massive blow to the broad property index, and subsequent weakness in</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743736-iyr-etf-overlooked-real-estate-fundamentals-technical-tailwinds-heading-into-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 06:33:16"}, {"id": "4743739", "title": "November CPI Report: Inflation Risks Keep The Fed On Edge", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with the words CPI on coins stack. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth with relate icon.\" data-id=\"1733234018\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Boy Wirat</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Seema Shah, Chief Global Strategist and Christian Floro, CFA, CMT, Market Strategist</em></p> <p>The November CPI report aligned with consensus expectations, likely confirming a Fed policy cut next week. Nevertheless, with monthly core inflation hitting its strongest rate since the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743739-november-cpi-report-inflation-risks-keep-fed-on-edge", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 06:20:00"}, {"id": "4743733", "title": "Ashtead Group: Near-Term Performance Is Uncertain, But Upside Remains Attractive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='A Sunbelt Rentals aerial lift against a clear blue sky. The green and white lift platform is raised high, indicating it\"s ready for use in construction.' data-id=\"2155939559\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"hi